---
title: Pork Salisbury Steak and Mash with Mushroom Gravy and Green Salad
description: We're breaking with tradition and making this classic with ground pork. With mushroom gravy, creamy mash and a refreshing side salad, we've got the hearty and the healthy all covered in one dish!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/porc-salisbury-et-puree-de-pommes-de-terre-0b4333c2.jpg
